questions.scenario:
You are debugging a production issue where a Spring Boot microservice crashes with an `OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space` during nightly batch processing. The following service is responsible for ingesting 100,000 records into the database: 

java
@Service
public class DataIngestor {
    @PersistenceContext
    private EntityManager entityManager;

    @Transactional
    public void processBatch(List<ExternalDto> inputs) {
        for (ExternalDto dto : inputs) {
            MetricEntity entity = new MetricEntity(dto);
            entityManager.persist(entity);
            // Logic to transform and link entities
        }
    }
}
